One fix is to add {{var}} before the function statement:

{code}
// this
var blah = function(e) {
	
};
// instead of this
blah = function(e) {
	
};
{code}

Or, to be consistent with the default Alloy template's {{onClick}} handler:

{code}
function fooBar(e) {

